{
  "stem": "14687.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Oh, I said to my sister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I said, I think we are going to go away from here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She say, come on, where are we going?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I say, I saw a-- a-- a carrier with two horses.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They were running so fast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we arrived there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was the selection that day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We arrived in the trains where they're taking out the people, you know, for working.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when we arrived there, the trains they were full.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They sent us back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The men, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we, all the people help like this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you're young, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you are afraid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you are ashamed of yourself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we used to do like this our face to get red a little bit not to go to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to say, one here, one here, one here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when my sister passed, and I was not near her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then after two, they took another one, and I passed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when I went out, and I embraced my sister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, oh, we are alive the two of us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was-- and we were crying all the time, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we were together all the time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the time we-- we passed through the selection, they took us to a factory from Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After six months-- after six months, we were there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nearly six months.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I saw my friends like Diamante Franco, the sister, and plenty of people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were already selected to the crematorium, who left them there, even my cousin [INAUDIBLE], So we left them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So in the night, they took us in the train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were crying in sickness.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like, we were going out in the morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
